column4: I have Universe and Multiverse enabled, but "wine" itself isn't in there.
There's wine-docs and a few frontends, but no core program.
for the wine thats the only place i would look
the wine repos could be down or busy
I don't know why it didn't work properly the first time around.
could have been a server issue
the only supported architecture is i386.
the auto-generated sources.list doesn't work too well.  ~_~
I guess I'm just special.  : D
